{"tid":2205951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你 !! 100 蚊港幣先唱到 40 蚊人仔, 天理何在 !!!","createTime":"2020-09-17T07:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T14:46:52.000Z","uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5504dd57db13869495478f2397da7a01206139","tid":2205951,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:17:46.000Z","msg":"成日話好人一世平安，唔知呢位先生，今日安好嗎？<br />\n時間返到四十幾年前，有一個媽媽一拖五個細路去到羅湖火車站，人生路不熟、人民幣未唱到，幾個細路又係咁嗌肚餓。呢個時候，一個好心人出現，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">塞咗40蚊人民幣俾呢位媽媽（仲係100蚊港紙先唱40蚊人民幣嘅年代）</span></strong></span>，叫佢快d買嘢俾細路食，唔肯收返錢，放低張卡片就走左。<br />\n一件好人好事，呢位住廣福既媽媽一直記喺心入面，佢今年已經80幾歲，希望有機會親口同呢個先生講聲多謝。當年張卡片都一直keep好喺銀包，可惜7個字既電話已經打唔通，廠亦都已經搬走埋。"},{"pid":"1d84ed538af1b0596bd4c2d39fc1b2a7c11ecff1","tid":2205951,"uid":203431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"前面加字2 3 5 6 9"},{"pid":"55f71ea1fdec9e51c271be8cd0829b4cdf0a3e59","tid":2205951,"uid":41437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"你嚟連登問、相都無張<br />\n80歲老人家會唔會上連登"},{"pid":"969ea0c1a2e1f136f1ea11b6f49fe950d4b922c3","tid":2205951,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f71ea1fdec9e51c271be8cd0829b4cdf0a3e59","tid":2205951,"uid":41437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"你嚟連登問、相都無張<br />\n80歲老人家會唔會上連登"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"搵到啦清"},{"pid":"9e6f1bbf2d3885a926fb42d033541c421d92606a","tid":2205951,"uid":49153,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"40年前唔係應該400蚊人仔先有100蚊港 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cc11dfb5493b8ce57f4369d1da3bbd5d746603","tid":2205951,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e6f1bbf2d3885a926fb42d033541c421d92606a","tid":2205951,"uid":49153,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T09: